Datasource.Parameter: ( SELECT geometry, area, type FROM osm_landusages ORDER BY area DESC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream') ) AS data

(SELECT geometry, type, 0 AS tunnel, 0 AS bridge, access, 'fill' AS render, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram','abandoned','disused') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other_rail' END AS stylegroup FROM osm_roads WHERE (type IS NOT NULL) AND (tunnel IS NULL OR tunnel = '0') AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge = '0') ORDER BY z_order ) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, bridge, tunnel FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk', 'primary', 'secondary', 'motorway_link', 'trunk_link')) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, bridge, tunnel FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk')) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, bridge, tunnel FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('rail')) AS data

(SELECT geometry, type, 1 AS bridge, access, render, layer, 0 as tunnel, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other' END AS stylegroup FROM ( SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '1_outline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge NOT IN ('0') UNION ALL SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '2_line' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge NOT IN ('0') UNION ALL SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '3_inline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge NOT IN ('0') ) AS bridges ORDER BY layer ASC, render ASC) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, name, name as iname, z_order, population FROM osm_places ORDER BY population DESC) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, name, ref, oneway, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') AND (name IS NOT NULL OR ref IS NOT NULL)) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, name, oneway FROM osm_roads WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR oneway IN ('yes','no')) AND type IN ('primary', 'secondary', 'tertiary')) AS data
(SELECT geometry, type, name, oneway FROM osm_roads WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR oneway IN ('yes','no')) AND type IN ('residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street', 'unknown')) AS data
